    dc:description "Figure 4. Liphistius choosaki sp. nov. female, ARA- 2019 - 057 (holotype) A dorsal view B, C vulva plate B ventral view C dorsal view. Abbreviations: CDO = central dorsal opening; GA = genital atrium; mm = millimeter; PP = poreplate; PS = posterior stalk; RC = receptacular cluster. Scale bars: 10 mm (A); 1 mm (B, C)." ;
